name: Cowboy Love is Pure 1-011: 1011 You Don't Know About Girls
description: Chapter 1, panel 11. A cowboy's fortune's are reversible and can be poorly founded. While he may have been seeking to be the better of a centipede, a centipede may prove to be the better of a cowboy. Stand, helpless, devoured by its shadow. A comic by Little Old Man. This panel is an edition of 30.
